 across all channels.\"}]},\"cta\":{\"title\":\"Transform Your Clinic with Virtual Practice\",\"subtitle\":\"Join thousands of healthcare providers who have revolutionized their practice with our all-in-one digital clinic platform.\",\"button_text\":\"Start Free 14-Day Trial\",\"button_link\":\"/register\",\"features_title\":\"Everything you need to succeed\",\"features_description\":\"Complete platform with AI documentation, comprehensive EHR, integrated billing, e-prescriptions, lab orders, patient engagement tools, and white-label branding - all in one solution.\",\"benefits\":[\"No credit card required\",\"Cancel anytime\"]}},\"white_label_solutions\":{\"meta\":{\"title\":\"White Label Telemedicine Platform - ContinuousCare | Healthcare Solutions\",\"description\":\"White label telemedicine platform with custom branding, mobile apps, and complete virtual care solutions. Launch your branded healthcare service quickly.\",\"og_title\":\"White Label Telemedicine Platform - ContinuousCare\",\"og_description\":\"White label telemedicine platform with custom branding, mobile apps, and complete virtual care solutions\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"White-Labeled Telemedicine Platform—\",\"title_highlight\":\"Under Your Brand\",\"subtitle\":\"Launch a fully branded healthcare app and portal with video consults, EHR, and patient engagement tools—no sign of ContinuousCare.\",\"benefits\":[\"Your Brand, Not Ours\",\"iOS \u0026 Android Apps Published in Your Accounts\",\"White-Labeled Telemedicine \u0026 Patient Engagement\",\"HIPAA \u0026 GDPR Compliant\"]},\"transform_section\":{\"title\":\"Transform Care Delivery with a White-Labeled Telemedicine Platform\",\"subtitle\":\"Launch your own branded healthcare app and portal in days—not months. With our white-label solution, everything from video consults to patient records runs under your name, logo, and domain—no trace of ContinuousCare. Delight patients, reduce development costs, and build lasting trust with a digital health expe